(Decision
    "persona-orchestrate is a real triad component — daemon + thin CLI + signal-persona-orchestrate ordinary contract + owner-signal-persona-orchestrate. Not folded into persona-mind. The component has been intended to exist for days; the design substance landing in /228 and onward is canonical, not exploratory."
